snippet.title: Arknights Official Concept Trailer 2
snippet.description:
They were named “The Infected”. They were born doomed. And… They need you, Doctor. 

Fight, in this endless night, until the dawn.

Official Discord Server:
https://discordapp.com/invite/arknights

Official Twitter Account:
https://twitter.com/ArknightsEN

Official Facebook Page:
https://www.facebook.com/ArknightsGlobal/

Official Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/arknights_messenger_official/

Arknights is a strategic RPG mobile game with a fantasy theme.

UNBECOMING 
Original Composer: Joshua Baker / Dustin Bates
OP: Josh Baker (Peer China) /Razor and Tie Music Publishing & True Anomaly Music (Concord Music)
SP : Peermusic (S.E. Asia) Ltd.


#Arknights #Yostar #Starset
